, 
<figureCitation id="3FE31E82FFDCFFBC623E156B564CE4FC" box="[517,531,634,655]" captionStart="FIGURES 4–6" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1432,1456]" captionTargetBox="[159,1427,322,1395]" captionTargetId="figure-67@3.[151,1436,309,1409]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 4–6. Female genital plates in caudal view of Monasavuhygia spp. 4, M. cordata Brailovsky, 1996. 5, M. fodina sp. nov. 6, M. incola sp. nov. FIGURES 7–9. Female genital plates in lateral view of Monasavuhygia spp. 7, M. cordata Brailovsky, 1996. 8, M. fodina sp. nov. 9, M. incola sp. nov." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5851263" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5851263/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="496">4</figureCitation>
